the Director General of NOSDRA, Mr. Musa, said the Agency was prepared to
partner the NNPC in mitigating oil spill in all areas of its oerations
stressing that the partnership would ensure a good operating environment for
the operators and the inhabitants. He
added that breaking of petroleum products pipelines did not provide food, water
and good environment for the people rather the malaise bleeds the national
purse of revenues that would have being used to provide developmental
infrastructure for the various tiers of government. He
